  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu (Spacetime)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 9 (Spell Level 5)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 4</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 24 | <b>Successes:</b> 6</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 12 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 26</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, E, H, Mas</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>This advanced form of Sennei Jashuu functions the same, except as above. The snakes have 30 ft range and take a -5 penalty to their attacks. Up to one snake can constrict a Tiny or smaller character, doubling for each size category larger (a Medium creature can be constricted by up to four snakes). After the snakes retract, you suffer 1d6 temporary Strength damage (Fortitude DC 19 negates).</p>\n\n<hr><p><b>Empower:</b> Spend 2 Chakra to summon an additional snake, up to 1 per level or 15 total (whichever is lower).</p>\n<p><b>Mastery:</b> The first through fourth steps decrease the Fortitude save DC to avoid Strength damage by 1. The fifth step removes the Strength damage entirely.</p>\n",
      "summary": "",
      "instructions": ""
    },
